|14|                  │ │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |item       |3       |6           |
|15|                  │ └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE RANGE SCAN |store_sales|2       |18          |
|16|                  └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET          |dt         |1       |18          |
==========================================================================================
